</title>




<para id="p1024">
Note the depressed pocket immediately to the right of the word 

<emphasis id="strong1033" effect="bold">
if

</emphasis>
 on 
the 

<emphasis id="strong1034" effect="bold">
if-else

</emphasis>
 block. We must drop another block of the correct shape 
into this pocket. The code in that block must evaluate to either true or 
false. 

