<para id="p1031">
We will refer to the first three blocks above as 

<emphasis id="strong1042" effect="bold">



<emphasis id="em1022" effect="italics">
relational 
operators

</emphasis>
</emphasis>
. 

<emphasis id="em1023" effect="italics">
