relational expression evaluates to false. 

<emphasis id="em1027" effect="italics">
(This relational expression 
is often referred to as a conditional clause.)

</emphasis>
. 

</para>




<para id="p1037">
However, we still 
haven't completed the conditional clause in 

<link id="a1067" target-id="Image_5">


Image 5

